type FinancialsDailySnapshot @entity @dailySnapshot {
  "Unique identifier for the financial snapshot."
  id: ID!
  "Reference to the yield aggregator protocol associated with the snapshot."
  protocol: YieldAggregator!
  "Total value locked in USD at the time of the snapshot."
  totalValueLockedUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Value controlled by the protocol in USD at the time of the snapshot."
  protocolControlledValueUSD: BigDecimal
  "Revenue generated for supply-side participants in USD for the day."
  dailySupplySideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative revenue generated for supply-side participants in USD up to the snapshot."
  cumulativeSupplySideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Revenue generated for the protocol in USD for the day."
  dailyProtocolSideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative revenue generated for the protocol in USD up to the snapshot."
  cumulativeProtocolSideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Total revenue generated in USD for the day."
  dailyTotalRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative total revenue generated in USD up to the snapshot."
  cumulativeTotalRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Block number at which the snapshot was taken."
  blockNumber: BigInt!
  "Timestamp indicating when the snapshot was taken."
  timestamp: BigInt!
}"}
